    "text": "# April 24, 2026  \n- Friday. Thank god the week is ending.\n- Preeti is much better today. The rest helped.\n- Neetish finished her history project. Submitted it online.\n- Mohan has a soccer match at school tomorrow.\n- Office: received promotion approval. Feeling excited.\n- Celebrated with the team in the evening.\n- Stopped at 56 Dukes on the way home. Bought pastries for the kids.\n- Browny waited at the door. Missed me, apparently.\n- Preeti cooked her special kadhi chawal for dinner.\n- Family movie night. Kids chose a cartoon. Browny fell asleep on the sofa.\n- End of a good week. Looking forward to the weekend.",
